# Domain Knowledge

## USTA League Structure

- Teams play ~10 matches per season against other clubs
- Each match has 5 lines: D1 (Doubles 1), D2, D3, S1 (Singles 1), S2
- D1 is worth **2 points** in 40+ leagues; all others worth 1 point
- Players have NTRP ratings (2.5 / 3.0 / 3.5 etc.)
- Matches are scraped from `leagues.ustanorcal.com` via `/api/admin/usta-sync`

